MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-1667. State ex rel. Kaine v. United Parcel Serv., Inc.

Franklin App. No. 93AP-843. On March 31, 1999, United Parcel Service, Inc. was ordered to show cause why its appeal should not be dismissed. United Parcel Service, Inc. has not filed a response to the show cause order. Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
